This library will help you to use trianglify with React.js :)`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "props"
    }}>{`Props`}</h2>
    <p>{`You can use all options from `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://github.com/qrohlf/trianglify"
      }}>{`trianglify`}</a>{` as props :)`}</p>
